INSERT IGNORE INTO `wp_wj2mzjsn96_postmeta` VALUES (2731, 164, 'speaker-biography', '<p>Dr. Holly Lucille entered the medical world driven by the simple desire to help bring people to a better place of wellness, but quickly became disillusioned with the reductionistic approach of the conventional medical world that sought to address any and all illness with a pre-packaged pill. Desiring a more personalized and supportive approach, Dr. Lucille found her calling in the naturopathic profession and has quickly become one of its leading experts, educators and advocates.</p><p>Alongside her private practice in Los Angeles, Dr. Lucille holds a position on the board of directors of AANP and has served as president of the California Naturopathic Doctors Association where she was among the frontline in the lobbying effort to get naturopathic doctors licensed in the state of California. An active promoter of the medicine across a variety of mediums, Dr. Lucille has appeared on television programs including Dr. Oz and The Doctors as well as appearing on national networks like Lifetime, The Hallmark Channel, and Discovery Fit &amp; Health and features in her own talk show, Myth Defying with Dr. Holly. Dr. Lucille has authored several books on integrative health, serves on the editorial advisory board of Natural Practitioner and Alternative Medicine and also hosts her radio show, Mindful Medicine.</p>'); 
INSERT IGNORE INTO `wp_wj2mzjsn96_postmeta` VALUES (2732, 164, 'speaker-blurb', 'Dr. Holly Lucille entered the medical world driven by the simple desire to help bring people and found her calling in the naturopathic profession. She has quickly become one of its leading experts, educators and advocates.'); 
