INSERT IGNORE INTO `wp_wj2mzjsn96_postmeta` VALUES (2880, 188, 'video-description', '<p>It’s easy to get wrapped up in the details. But when it comes to naturopathic medicine, Dr. Holly Lucille knows better than to put the parts before the whole.</p><h3>The Interview</h3><p>When you\'re first starting out, I think it\'s easy to do remedial training. You hear why somebody might be coming in to see you and you go and read your books and flesh out all the differential diagnosis. But don\'t. Don\'t worry. Just be present and be with them, because a lot of times, people don\'t even know why they\'re coming in. When they are coming to see us, they are coming for so much more than what they think and what you think, but you\'ve got to be able to be present in order to actually feel that and pick that up.</p>'); 
