INSERT IGNORE INTO `wp_wj2mzjsn96_postmeta` VALUES (2964, 135, 'video-description', '<p>Dr. Moira Fitzpatrick believes in the integration of natural and conventional treatments. She’s brought this belief to her own practice, where she collaborates with a conventional medical doctor to create a unique plan for each patient.</p><h3>The Interview</h3><p>I\'m Moira Fitzpatrick, and I\'m a naturopathic doctor and also a licensed clinical psychologist. <strong>One of the things that I\'m committed to doing is building bridges with conventional medicine because I believe that integrative medicine offers individual\'s choice</strong> about what it is that they need to do at this particular point in their life and what their needs are. I\'ve been fortunate enough to work in a practice where there is a conventional medical doctor and myself. One of the lovely things about this practice is the two of us are seeing patients together. <strong>We create an integrative treatment plan that is just superlative for this individual</strong>, and they love it. They love the idea of a conventional doctor working with a natural medicine doctor. We have the foundation, but <strong>we need our colleagues, we need our integrative medical doctors, we need our conventional medical doctors,</strong> and I think we have to be the ones that take the high road and reach out and become the teachers, because <strong>we have the depth, the principles, the knowhow and hopefully the openness and flexibility.</strong></p>'); 
